Activity 1: Creating Course Object

To create an object:
1. From the Setup page
2. Click on Object Manager
3. Click on Create >> Custom Object
4. Enter the Label name as Course
5. Enter Plural Label name as Courses
6. Enter Record Name as Course Name
7. Select Data Type Text
8. Select Allow Reports
9. Select Allow Search
10. Enable Track Field History
11. Click on Save and New


Activity 2: Creating Student Enrollment Object

To create an object:
From the Setup page
Click on Object Manager
Click on Create >> Custom Object
Enter the Label name as Student Enrollment
Enter Plural Label name as Student Enrollments
Enter Record Name as Student Enrollment ID
Select Data Type as Auto Number: SE - {0000}, Starting with 1
Select Allow Reports
Select Allow Search
Enable Track Field History · Click on Save
